		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Anyone know if the Super Famicom uses the same motherboard as the SNES?<br />From the images I've seen they look identical.<br /><br />I'm aware that the SNES went through revisions where they moved the sound module onto the motherboard at some point. So that is the only known factor I'm aware of.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
